LCS/databases/PL: Version 1.1, date: 2006/02/07
===============================================

This is the first minor release of the major release 1 of the PL package.
No significant changes were made to the code. However, substantial changes
have been made to the directory structure. 

In order to make PL distributable, all header files have been moved to the
`include/PL' directory. Furthermore, the scripts from the PLGEN package were
merged with the PL package and placed in the `scripts' directory.



LCS/databases/PL: Version 1.0, date: 2004/09/21
===============================================

This is the first official release of the PL package.

* The Query classes are now part of the PL package.
